# i18n

- All user-visible strings via translation keys (`labelKey`, `titleKey`, `| translate`).
- Add every new key to **both** `public/assets/en.json` and `public/assets/bh.json` (single file per language).
- In TS, return key strings for labels (e.g. `statusLabel()` → `'portal.user.features.cargo.table.cargoTypes.${type}'`).
- Do not embed English prose in templates when a key exists or should exist.

## Key tree (mirrors `src/app/` layers)

```
shared.*                          — shell chrome + form/table/confirm frameworks
guest.*                           — public pages (landing, sign-in, login, register)
portal.shell.{admin|user}.*   — portal badge in sidebar brand
portal.admin.nav.*                — admin sidebar
portal.admin.pages.*              — admin route page header ({ title, subtitle })
portal.admin.features.<feature>.* — admin feature (form, table)
portal.user.nav.*             — user sidebar
portal.user.pages.*           — user route page header ({ title, subtitle })
portal.user.features.<domain>.<feature>.* — user feature (form, table)
```

### Shared (`shared.*`)

| Path | Use for |
|------|---------|
| `shared.sidebar.*` | Portal sidebar chrome |
| `shared.topbar.*` | Portal + shared topbar widgets (theme, language, account) |
| `shared.form.common.*` | Form footer (`previous`, `next`), stepper pill aria (`validationState.*`), leave-form discard dialog (`discardChanges.*`), field errors (`errors.*` incl. `minDate`, `dateRange`) |
| `shared.table.common.*` | Table loading, empty, emptyFiltered, pagination, row actions |
| `shared.table.filters.*` | Filter panel toggle, chips, multi-select, sliders, units (`kg`, `m²`) |
| `shared.route.*` | Shared route UI copy (`fromTo` aria-label for `RouteDisplayComponent`) |
| `shared.vehicle.*` | Shared vehicle UI copy (`namePlate` aria-label for `VehicleDisplayComponent`) |
| `shared.warehouse.*` | Shared warehouse UI copy (`nameCity` aria-label for `WarehouseDisplayComponent`) |
| `shared.dateRange.*` | Shared date range UI copy (`fromTo`, `single` aria-labels for `DateRangeDisplayComponent`) |
| `shared.entityStatus.*` | Shared status pill labels for `StatusBadgeComponent` (interim — user routes/cargo/storage); per-entity keys later under `portal.*.features.<entity>.status.*` |

Table **merged period** column headers: `portal.user.features.routes.table.columns.period`, `portal.user.features.storage.table.columns.period` (distinct from form field keys like `transportStartDate`).

Table **filter labels**: `portal.user.features.<entity>.table.filters.*`; section groups: `…table.filterGroups.{route|attributes|dates|location}`.
| `shared.confirm.common.*` | Confirmation dialog cancel/confirm button labels (defaults; do not duplicate per feature) |

### Guest (`guest.*`)

| Path | Use for |
|------|---------|
| `guest.landing.*` | Landing page |
| `guest.signIn.*` | Portal picker |
| `guest.login.*` | User + admin login pages |
| `guest.register.*` | Company registration page chrome |
| `guest.register.form.*` | Register company stepper form |
| `guest.topbar.*`, `guest.footer.*` | Guest shell |

